      • tile

        public Tile tile(int x,
        int y)
        Returns a tile at the specified offsets into the coverage.

        The fill(TileDataset) method must be called before this method is called. The x and y values are specified relative to the lower left corner of the tile cover. Meaning x = 0, y = 0 is the most lower left tile in ths cover.
